(MEI 148460 ). Dark brown. Sternite 8 (Fig. 28 ) quadrate, posterior margin broadly rounded; setae dark brown, continuous across posterior margin. Gonocoxite ventral view (Fig. 28 ), posterior margin sinuate then extending posterolaterally to pointed projection, setae dark brown. Aedeagus lateral view (Fig. 29 ) thick, apex short, sinuate; ejaculatory apodeme lateral view (Fig. 29 ) pale brown, anterior margin paler, anterior half clavate.
